  <h3><b>To provide writers with a means of self-discipline to aid them in all writing endeavors. </b></h3>
  <div class="jumbotron">
<p> We created an application with the aim of helping all those who use writing platforms to maintain focus and discipline whilst writing. In the modern day, there are constant distractions on one's computer and devices that allow for plenty of excuses to avoid writing and thus, cause missed deadlines and due dates for students, authors, and all others who write on a consistent basis.</p>
</div>
<h4><b>About the Founder</b> </h4>
<br>
<div class="jumbotron">
